@Generated(value="com.guidewire.pl.metadata.codegen.Codegen", comments="ClaimSearchView.eti;ClaimSearchView.eix;ClaimSearchView.etx") public class ClaimSearchView extends ClaimAssignmentView implements KeyableBean, ArchivedClaimCompatible
ClaimSearchView Supports the efficient creation of claim lists returned through ClaimCenter's search function. This is a virtual entity and is not stored in the database.
